82-1238792#:~:text=Slipknot%20drummer%20Joey%20Jordison%20has,exit%20in%20the%20near%20future.">2013 年 12 月离开的</a>原鼓手 Joey Jordison。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknots-founding-drummer-joey-jordison-has-died-at-46-3004210">乔迪森于 2021 年去世，享年 46 岁</a>。</p><p>多年来，乐队经历了多次人员变动，包括 2019 年 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-percussionist-chris-fehn-suing-rest-band-2462222">迈克尔·普法夫 (Michael Pfaff) 取代了打击乐手克里斯·费恩 (Chris Fehn)</a> 。此前，贝斯手 Alessandro Venturella 接替了 2010 年去世的 Paul Gray。最近，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-are-seemingly-teasing-a-new-member-3452721">长期键盘手 Craig Jones 于 6 月离开了乐队</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-shuts-down-speculation-on-new-slipknot-drummer-3549794">科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor) 驳回了有关新活结鼓手的猜测的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
四人春节向战争儿童捐赠未发行专辑《⣎⡇ꉺლ༽இ•̛)ྀ◞ ༎ຶ ༽ৣৢٞৢме ꉺლ》的黑胶唱片https://www.nme.com/news/music/four-tet-donates-vinyl-copy-of-unreleased-album-%e2%a3%8e%e2%a1%87%ea%89%ba%e1 %83%9a%e0%bc%bd%e0%ae%87%cc%9b%e0%be%80%e2%97%9e-%e0%bc%8e%e0%ba%b6-%e0%bc %bd%e0%a7%a3%e0%a7%a2%d8%9e%e0%a7%a2-3549774?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=四-tet-捐赠-乙烯基-未发行专辑-% 25e2%25a3%258e%25e2%25a1%2587%25ea%2589%25ba%25e1%2583%259a%25e0%25bc%25bd%25e0%25ae%2587%25cc%259b%25e0%25be%2580%25e2%2597% 259e-%25e0%25bc%258e%25e0%25ba%25b6-%25e0%25bc%25bd%25e0%25a7%25a3%25e0%25a7%25a2%25d8%259e%25e0%25a7%25a2Emma Wilkes Mon, 27 Nov 2023 22:08:03 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronic https://www.nme.com/?p=3549774 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="春节四" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在发行了几次测试版后，只有少数歌迷能够听到这张专辑</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/four-tet-donates-vinyl-copy-of-unreleased-album-%e2%a3%8e%e2%a1%87%ea%89%ba%e1%83%9a%e0%bc%bd%e0%ae%87%cc%9b%e0%be%80%e2%97%9e-%e0%bc%8e%e0%ba%b6-%e0%bc%bd%e0%a7%a3%e0%a7%a2%d8%9e%e0%a7%a2-3549774">四节春节后向 War Child 捐赠未发行专辑“⣎⡇ꉺლ༽இ•̛)ྀ◞ ༎ຶ ༽ৣৢٞৢמז ꉺლ”的黑胶唱片首先出现在 NME 上</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="春节四" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Four-Tet-Lovebox-2019-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/four-tet">四岁春节</a>将他的未发行专辑“⣎⡇ꉺლ༽இ•̛)ྀ◞ ༎ຶ ༽ৣৢÞৢמז ꉺლ”的黑胶唱片捐赠给了 Resident Advisor 的慈善抽奖活动。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/skrillex-live-in-new-york-city-a-once-in-a-lifetime-rave-at-the-garden-3401021">Skrillex 纽约现场评论：一生一次的狂欢</a></strong></li></ul><p>尽管向歌迷发送了一些试压，这张创作于 2021 年的专辑从未正式发行。抽奖所得将捐赠给战争儿童组织，该组织帮助生活在全球冲突中的儿童。</p><p>上周末，Resident Advisor 和 War Child 面向音乐产业的筹款平台“舞蹈权”在哈克尼威克举办了一个现场慈善唱片店，多位艺术家捐赠唱片进行出售。铁三角转盘和设备也在抽奖活动中可供争夺。</p><p>四人春节在 2023 年举办了一场盛大的演出，经常与其他制作人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skrillex">Skrillex</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred Again 进行现场合作。</a>三人进行了许多备受瞩目的演出，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/skrillex-live-in-new-york-city-a-once-in-a-lifetime-rave-at-the-garden-3401021">在麦迪逊广场花园举行的一场门票全部售完的演出</a>以及在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/skrillex-fred-again-four-tet-coachella-2023-3433669">科切拉音乐节的闭幕演出。</a>向 100,000 多人展示。一月份，他们还在伦敦的 Electric Ballroom、Electric Brixton 和 Troxy 举办了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/skrillex-fred-again-and-four-tet-announce-third-last-minute-london-gig-tonight-3376327">三场亲密的演出</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3034177" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3034177" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3034177" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/four-tet-kieran-hebden-live.jpg" alt="基兰·赫布登四岁春节" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/four-tet-kieran-hebden-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/four-tet-kieran-hebden-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/four-tet-kieran-hebden-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/four-tet-kieran-hebden-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/four-tet-kieran-hebden-live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/four-tet-kieran-hebden-live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3034177" class="wp-caption-text">四元春节 图片来源：Matthew Baker/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>然而，几个月前，他对自己“终于获得了应有的成功”的想法提出了质疑。</p><p> “在科切拉音乐节之后，我就想到了这个想法——‘他终于获得了他应得的成功’——但实际上并不是那样的感觉，”他对<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2023/aug/11/100000-people-are-about-to-lose-their-minds-four-tet-on-being-the-worlds-unlikeliest-superstar-dj" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>说。</p><p> “我参加了 Coachella 音乐节，下一场演出是在我女儿 13 岁生日派对上为 20 名十几岁的女孩表演了一场长达 3 个半小时的演出，我觉得她们一直在深深地看着我。”</p><p>他继续说道，尽管举办了这些大型演出，但他发现很难相信自己将来能够向如此众多的观众演出。</p><p> “我想说我不知道​​我是否会再次参加科切拉音乐节这样的活动，”他补充道。 “但我和桑尼 [Moore，又名 Skrillex] 正在为洛杉矶 75,000 人带来艰难的夏季。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/four-tet-donates-vinyl-copy-of-unreleased-album-%e2%a3%8e%e2%a1%87%ea%89%ba%e1%83%9a%e0%bc%bd%e0%ae%87%cc%9b%e0%be%80%e2%97%9e-%e0%bc%8e%e0%ba%b6-%e0%bc%bd%e0%a7%a3%e0%a7%a2%d8%9e%e0%a7%a2-3549774">四节春节后向 War Child 捐赠未发行专辑“⣎⡇ꉺლ༽இ•̛)ྀ◞ ༎ຶ ༽ৣৢٞৢמז ꉺლ”的黑胶唱片首先出现在 NME 上</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ;
聆听 Villagers 和 Lisa Hannigan 翻唱的“The Little Drummer Boy” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-villagers-and-lisa-hannigans-cover-of-the-little-drummer-boy-3549766?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-村民和丽莎·汉尼根斯封面的小鼓手男孩Anagricel DuranMon, 27 Nov 2023 21:48:30 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3549766 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="村民和丽莎·汉尼根的“小鼓手男孩”艺术作品。图片来源：新闻界" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “从我还是个小男孩的时候起，凯瑟琳·肯尼科特·戴维斯的这首歌比任何其他圣诞颂歌都更能激发我的想象力”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-villagers-and-lisa-hannigans-cover-of-the-little-drummer-boy-3549766">Listen to Villagers 和 Lisa Hannigan 翻唱的《The Little Drummer Boy》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="村民和丽莎·汉尼根的“小鼓手男孩”艺术作品。图片来源：新闻界" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/villagers-little-drummer-boy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/villagers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">村民们</a>与歌手丽莎·汉尼根 (Lisa Hannigan) 合作翻唱了圣诞经典歌曲《小鼓手男孩》(The Little Drummer Boy) - 请查看下面的内容。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/villagers-fever-dreams-review-3021407">村民——《狂热之梦》评论：昏昏欲睡、迷幻的灵魂召唤出另一个世界</a></strong></li></ul><p>这支爱尔兰独立民谣乐队宣布将于 2024 年 6 月 29 日在都柏林三一学院举办迄今为止规模最大的头条演出，随后翻唱了这首宁静的节日歌曲。</p><p>在新闻发布会上谈到歌曲选择时，Villages 乐队主唱康纳·奥布莱恩 (Conor O&#39;Brien) 表示：“从我还是个小男孩的时候起，凯瑟琳·肯尼科特·戴维斯 (Katherine Kennicott Davis) 的这首歌比任何其他圣诞颂歌都更能激发我的想象力。与丽莎·汉尼根无与伦比的声音一起表演这真是一个梦想。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="村民和丽莎·汉尼根 - 小鼓手男孩（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hVgJ-qJGyH0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《小鼓手男孩》由凯瑟琳·肯尼科特·戴维斯 (Katherine Kennicott Davis) 于 1941 年创作，原名《鼓的卡罗尔》(Carol Of The Drum)，现已成为节日必备歌曲。许多人猜测这首歌大致是根据捷克颂歌“Hajej，nynjej”改编的。</p><p>在接受戴维斯母校韦尔斯利学院音乐系主任克莱尔·方泰恩 (Claire Fontijn) 采访时，方泰恩透露，《小鼓手男孩》的灵感来自于 1941 年的戴维斯。</p><p> “[有一天]，当她想小睡时，她脑海中浮现出这首歌，这首歌的灵感应该是来自一首法语歌曲《Patapan》，然后将“Patapan”翻译成法语她的大脑发出“帕-朗姆-砰-砰”的声音，并呈现出一种节奏。结果就是《小鼓手男孩》，”Fontijn 说。</p><p>最著名的圣诞颂歌翻唱是宾<a href="/artists/bing-crosby">·克劳斯比 (Bing Crosby)</a>和<a href="/artists/david-bowie">大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie)</a>的翻唱。这首歌曲名为“Peace on Earth/Little Drummer Boy”，于 1977 年为 Crosby 的电视特别节目<em>Bing Crosby 的 Merrie Olde Christmas 录制。</em></p><p>在这首歌中，克罗斯比演唱了《小鼓手男孩》，而鲍伊则加入了《地球上的和平》，这首歌曲是由该特别节目的音乐总监伊恩·弗雷泽、拉里·格罗斯曼和编剧布兹·科汉专门为此次合作创作的。这首二重唱是克罗斯比 1977 年 10 月去世前的最后一张唱片。</p><p> 《Peace On Earth/Little Drummer Boy》于 1982 年由 RCA 唱片公司作为单曲发行，并取得了商业上的成功，在英国单曲榜上排名第三。这是克罗斯比最后一首流行歌曲，并成为鲍伊职业生涯中最畅销的单曲之一。该单曲在英国的总销量预计超过 40 万张。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="宾·克罗斯比 (Bing Crosby)、大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie) - 地球和平 / 小鼓手男孩" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lCpXMy5GalI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这首二重唱已成为美国、英国和加拿大圣诞节的主打歌曲，并被<a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/2006/12/20/bing-and-bowie-an-odd-story-of-holiday-harmony/15576902-5854-4eec-9d38-9d2e5b820920/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《华盛顿邮报》</em></a>称为“圣诞音乐史上最成功的二重唱之一”。</p><p>在其他圣诞新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iconic-the-snowman-david-bowie-scarf-now-for-sale-3537718">鲍伊在 1982 年改编的<em>《雪人》</em>的著名介绍中曾经佩戴过的雪人围巾的复制品</a>现在可以购买。</p><p>这条传奇围巾的售价为 19.99 英镑，灵感源自鲍伊在拍摄<em>《雪人》</em>简介时在自家阁楼上佩戴的那条围巾，当时动画首次在美国播出。</p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad0 id_ad_content-horiz-center">多年来，深受喜爱的圣诞动画的粉丝们一直在寻找这件衣服，鲍伊的儿子邓肯·琼斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/producer-shares-heartwarming-story-behind-david-bowie-the-snowman-scarf-2845119">去年重新发现了原来的围巾</a>。</div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-villagers-and-lisa-hannigans-cover-of-the-little-drummer-boy-3549766">Listen to Villagers 和 Lisa Hannigan 翻唱的《The Little Drummer Boy》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
