 Skepta 宣布将于 2024 年夏季举办首届 Big Smoke Festival https://www.nme.com/news/music/skepta-announces-inaugural-big-smoke-festival-for-summer-2024-3549754?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=skepta-announces-inaugural-big-smoke- 2024 年夏季音乐节Emma WilkesMon, 27 Nov 2023 21:19:39 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3549754 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="斯克普塔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Skepta 将策划两阶段音乐节的阵容</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/skepta-announces-inaugural-big-smoke-festival-for-summer-2024-3549754">Skepta 宣布 2024 年夏季首届 Big Smoke Festival 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="斯克普塔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-press-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skepta">Skepta</a>宣布举办首届一日音乐节 Big Smoke。</p><p><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/skepta-ignorance-is-bliss-review-2503032">Skepta – “无知就是幸福”评论</a></strong></p><p>新活动将于 7 月 6 日星期六在伦敦东南部的水晶宫公园举行，阵容由 Skepta 亲自策划。</p><p>这位说唱歌手将在两个露天舞台上选择表演，其中一个将由他的唱片公司 Más Tiempo 和平台舞蹈艺术家主持。</p><p> Skepta 也将进行表演，这是他 2024 年在英国的唯一一场演出。其余阵容将在适当的时候公布。 </p><figure id="attachment_3549770" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3549770" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3549770" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-mike-amrsland-1.jpg" alt="斯克普塔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-mike-amrsland-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-mike-amrsland-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-mike-amrsland-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-mike-amrsland-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-mike-amrsland-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/skepta-mike-amrsland-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3549770" class="wp-caption-text">斯克普塔。图片来源：迈克·马斯兰/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>Skepta 在 Instagram 上现场透露了这一消息，他说：“我很高兴终于宣布 Big Smoke Festival 正式成立。我很兴奋，这样做真是太疯狂了。”我只想对所有支持者说声谢谢，你们已经好几年没有在舞台上看到我了。我知道很多人都想知道什么时候能在音乐节上看到 Skepta，我真的我想节省所有的精力，并将其投入到为我们、由我们自己做的事情中。”</p><p>他继续说道：“将会有一个现场舞台，展示所有你最喜欢的表演——任何你认识的与 Skepta 相关的人。一侧将有一个现场舞台，而 Más Tiempo 舞台也将有完整的阵容。我可能会破坏一个舞台，飞到另一个舞台并与 Jammer 连接。这会很疯狂。”</p><p>门票将于周五（12 月 1 日）开始发售——您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fskepta-tickets%2Fartist%2F1580036" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。</p><p>上周，Skepta<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/skepta-shares-new-ep-48-hours-with-ryder-3548967">发行了与 Ryder 合作的 EP《48 小时》</a> 。 19 岁的 Ryder 于 10 月份在 TikTok 上分享了他对 Skepta 的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-skepta-16466-306100">Konnichiwa</a> ”深切“Text Me Back”的混音，名为“#skeptacore pt.”。 3&#39;。自病毒式传播并获得超过 100 万次观看次数以来，伦敦 grime 传奇人物已正式与赫尔的制作人合作，发行了一张五首曲目的 EP。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/skepta-announces-inaugural-big-smoke-festival-for-summer-2024-3549754">Skepta 宣布 2024 年夏季首届 Big Smoke Festival 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
